wsdl:definitions.wsdl:documentation: Webservice used to export Skarabee publications to a Skarabee Agents website.

wsdl:operation.name: GetPublicationSummaries
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Get publication summaries for publications that where last created/modified after the given date. lastModified not specified will return all active publications. RequestedPropertyTypes (PropertyTypes) not specified will return all allowed types. Please use RequestedPropertyTypes instead of PropertyTypes, PropertyTypes will be removed in future versions.

wsdl:operation.name: GetContactInfo
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Get contact info of current agent.

wsdl:operation.name: GetProjectSummaries
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Get an overview of all active projects, when lastmodified is not supplied, or all active and modified projects, when lastmodified is supplied. Projects/properties are nested like this: project>models>lots>transactions. Only properties that are published will contain a ProjectPropertyPublication.

wsdl:operation.name: GetLogins
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation: Get all login info for every user that can publish to you.

wsdl:service.name: Skarabee_x0020_Web_x0020_Link
wsdl:service.wsdl:documentation: Webservice used to export Skarabee publications to a Skarabee Agents website.
